{"title":"春的掌声","authors":["张秋实"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":4,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的掌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张秋实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮在望，春潮在望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的掌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一如那绿叶初乍的音韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在霑霑的春雨里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由远而近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的掌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一如那柳笛汩汩流淌的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由远而近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的掌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似春燕的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裁剪着雨后的长空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的掌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"润湿了共和国的每一扇小窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也润湿了我的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，掌声响起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要再一次告诉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生我养我的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是没有根据的欢乐呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问春风问子规"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问民心问土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问正在吐芽的种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问正在奋长着的春心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，再问问"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我这颗改变不了的中国心吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨，滴滴嗒嗒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮在望，春潮在望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，掌声响起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮合着脉搏的节拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起撞击着堤岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我依偎着阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用舒缓的歌喉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叙说着一个属于中国的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我以拥抱的姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再一次亲近着春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一如那绿柳亲吻春风般地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲吻着拍岸的浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮在望，春潮在望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，掌声响起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我悄悄告诉你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我悄悄告诉你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心里，他的心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一位国人的心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在生长着一个秘密"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个绿色的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在跃起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正像一个农人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼望一个久久的希冀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在自己的田头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着自己亲手种下的未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由枯转绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骄傲地吮着烟袋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再以一个农人满足的眼神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝视着田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，悠闲地品味着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熏香而又丰稔的信息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮在望，春潮在望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，掌声响起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌声响起来"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}